<refnamediv>
<refname>pgrphack</refname>
<refpurpose>runs a program in a separate process group</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
<cmdsynopsis>
<command>pgrphack</command>
<arg choice='req'><replaceable>child</replaceable></arg>
</cmdsynopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsection>
<title>Description</title>

<para>
<command>pgrphack</command> runs <replaceable>child</replaceable> in a new process group.
</para>

</refsection>

